svg.title: Mythonancial.2
svg.text: The game is structured to be in multiple levels, where each level teaches and quizzes the player on a new topic of investments. This allows a fun and natural learning flow for the player.

Each level has two parts to it: the learninng part and the boss part. In the learning part, the player accompanies Pecunia to learn about that level’s topic. She utilizes important facts and data in order to fully immerse the player in the vital aspects of that topic.
